{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"317f92bc6c","title":"“关于统战政策”的言论","origin":"中共厦门大学委员会宣传部编印《右派反动言论集》，1957年9月20日。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"dbdd6a8ea1","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"317f92bc6c"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"d0fe9c9b0e","name":"厦门大学师生"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"7cd92e9846","type":"title","text":"“关于统战政策”的言论","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"317f92bc6c"},{"id":"8318701c08","type":"authors","text":"厦门大学师生","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"317f92bc6c"},{"id":"04c24345c0","type":"paragraph","text":"陈碧笙：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"317f92bc6c"},{"id":"2a5c831356","type":"paragraph","text":"“民主党派要三权：(1)用人权，a．民主党派对其参加政府的成员自己要有决定权。b．民主党派对其干部和成员有鉴定权。(2)财政权，(3)发言权，a．起政治设计作用，b．自己办报。”","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"317f92bc6c"},{"id":"c6f6beb689","type":"paragraph","text":"林兴中：","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"317f92bc6c"},{"id":"80b9ca9b35","type":"paragraph","text":"“把民主人士的副总理迁到人大常委去，这是‘有棺材无灵位’。”","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"317f92bc6c"},{"id":"6268ed2a15","type":"paragraph","text":"李栋松：","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"317f92bc6c"},{"id":"06f1f45f2e","type":"paragraph","text":"“如果我做总统，要给所有的民主党派充分的自由”。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"317f92bc6c"},{"id":"de33fc22e9","type":"paragraph","text":"陈今：","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"317f92bc6c"},{"id":"9e15169460","type":"paragraph","text":"“在我思想中民主党派与我差不多。”“民主党派应该取消，充实工会、工商联，或组织老人协会，因为民主党派不是在野党而是架床叠架。”","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"317f92bc6c"},{"id":"bdef3191ee","type":"paragraph","text":"历史系吴建华：","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"317f92bc6c"},{"id":"4607ca8c74","type":"paragraph","text":"“民主党派给党挟死了，会老不会大。民主党派在统战部好象花瓶，是排好看的。”","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"317f92bc6c"},{"id":"b6a2d4ba17","type":"paragraph","text":"历史系陈遂良：","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"317f92bc6c"},{"id":"1c268aae0f","type":"paragraph","text":"“民主党派给党挟得死死，不能发展，顶多只吸收旧社会的人，会老不会大。”","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"317f92bc6c"},{"id":"6b2a0e2626","type":"paragraph","text":"“党对民主党派不相信，限制多，无权无作用，统战部坐交椅是排排好看；共存共不起来，监督也监不起来。”","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"317f92bc6c"},{"id":"172c4be915","type":"paragraph","text":"“统战形式共处议政、多数表决，这是合乎民主的，才是真正的统战精神和内容，民主党派的作用才看得出，共产党的错误才会减少。”","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"317f92bc6c"},{"id":"050e814d6a","type":"paragraph","text":"化学系邓家余：“开口时是需要你们，现在党的干部多了，就慢慢地把你们(民主党派)踢出去。民主党派是阿斗，只管拿扫帚打苍蝇。”","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"317f92bc6c"},{"id":"5b132fe7e2","type":"paragraph","text":"历史系邹日升：","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"317f92bc6c"},{"id":"1caf055f33","type":"paragraph","text":"“现在除党以外都是有职无权，挂个空名。”","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"317f92bc6c"},{"id":"c33e981c09","type":"paragraph","text":"数学系邓锡宏：","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"317f92bc6c"},{"id":"aa7219eb51","type":"paragraph","text":"“政协、人代是傀儡，只是做政治上的花瓶，不能代表人民说话，什么决议都只是将党中央指示的东西拿来通过一下，根本没有什么作用。”","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"317f92bc6c"}],"page":{"id":"dd8f8d6a77","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"317f92bc6c","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}